{"tid":383370,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"兩歲BB被氣槍射穿頭","createTime":"2017-09-01T12:06:22.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-01T12:23:41.000Z","uid":36494,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"89cfbe12ec5f47b1e4a7bdda08abb023622cbb68","tid":383370,"uid":36494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T12:06:22.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20170901&amp;s=10829391&amp;a=57156181\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20170901%26s%3D10829391%26a%3D57156181&d=Od297faog6gO%2BNk5sSXTTwCO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=35016b96\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20170901%26s%3D10829391%26a%3D57156181&h=b2821c19\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20170901&amp;s=10829391&amp;a=57156181</a><br />\n【氣槍狂徒】囝囝需休養一周 B媽冀盡快拘捕兇徒<br />\n<br />\n郭太續稱，與丈夫5年前搬入和明苑，兩年前誕下蝦仔後，幾乎每天都會帶兒子落樓下公園玩兩次，郭太坦言從沒聽聞有人亂射氣槍，昨午約12時35分，郭太如常帶蝦仔到位於明德邨明覺樓對開花槽附近睇雀仔，蝦仔當時踩著一架滑板車仔，「突然個仔大喊，然後向後跌，我上前睇，發現額頭位流晒血，我以為畀雀仔啄。」<br />\n<br />\n她第一時間抱蝦仔到附近西醫診所求診，但西醫指傷口深且大，像是外物造成，建議立即到急診室縫針。「急症室醫生話個傷口有成5mm至1cm深，而且係圓形，估計係膠子彈或鋼子彈造成都有可能。」醫生先用膠水將蝦仔額前的皮膚黏合，然後照電腦掃瞄，幸好沒有大礙。"},{"pid":"487cb08aeee32becb36b835b1b9144adf82f6191","tid":383370,"uid":57962,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T12:06:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"88952ca4a38c28d86de9bf6aa7b9e0553737d801","tid":383370,"uid":36494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T12:07:41.000Z","msg":"由於案情嚴重，大批警察機動部隊警員昨晚到明德邨的事發現場搜索，初步找到數粒bb彈子彈。將軍澳警區重案組跟進調查，暫未有人被捕。"},{"pid":"a015032e6645b91dae65717a4b432085f160cfc5","tid":383370,"uid":119450,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T12:07:45.000Z","msg":"仆街還仆街，但真係幾準"},{"pid":"591b9618e6910e0e1e6d41deb80c5375139fd7c4","tid":383370,"uid":3037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T12:08:52.000Z","msg":"膠水痴返個頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ebe722900d233d16ca3a44342f39f20638a2443c","tid":383370,"uid":36494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T12:08:52.000Z","msg":"將軍澳有兩歲男童，在明德邨商場對開空地玩耍時，前額中槍淌血。據悉，當時母親因擔心不已，急抱著男童往商場的診所求醫。負責看診的陳家耀醫生憶述稱，見男童右邊額頭有0.5cm的傷口，「佢好清醒，有血流出嚟，於是叫佢即刻去急症室。」他指出，當時男童母親向他表示，兒子只是向後跌，不明白為何前面有傷口。陳醫生表示，在上址開診所約20年，未試過有人「中槍」向他求診。"},{"pid":"770902d796d3f3c0cfb72a37b673c8afb9da0d7d","tid":383370,"uid":29645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T12:09:03.000Z","msg":"咩膠水？"},{"pid":"c2dc564a3e789a214dbe46cf3f9d2e97f1976714","tid":383370,"uid":36494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T12:11:14.000Z","msg":"Skin glue is a special type of medical adhesive. It joins the edges of a wound together, while the wound starts to heal underneath.<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.nhs.uk/chq/Pages/2552.aspx?CategoryID=72\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.nhs.uk%2Fchq%2FPages%2F2552.aspx%3FCategoryID%3D72&d=Od297faog6gO%2BNk5sSXTTwCO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=7105ecb0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.nhs.uk/chq/Pages/2552.aspx?CategoryID=72</a>"},{"pid":"2e30e8419d5c4dd45bae3528cccf65a060bf737f","tid":383370,"uid":90643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T12:16:15.000Z","msg":"諗起大陸禁氣槍單野"},{"pid":"96da3c0c3c16968c518cdaec6f3f9fdf41f1b0f9","tid":383370,"uid":32906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T12:20:45.000Z","msg":"諗起俄佬爆頭仲笑騎騎果張圖"},{"pid":"33b3b547a5bf9802eb4640d8756f57251632abdf","tid":383370,"uid":68796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T12:21:40.000Z","msg":"傑志總領隊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0adade711a4f62add28bd250e76c44c468ad24e8","tid":383370,"uid":2054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T12:22:58.000Z","msg":"headshot terrorist win"},{"pid":"2b6b6f907d9a4e53488435607f42f6aa64855638","tid":383370,"uid":85163,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T12:23:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}